{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015KKnEobtSz3mC5aLReURAw","type":"tool_result","content":"Starting PostgreSQL version 16...\nCREATE ROLE\nCREATE DATABASE\nGRANT\nBuilding Quarkus application...\nStarting the Quarkus application...\nWaiting for application to start...\n2026-03-14 07:36:05,239 INFO  [io.quarkus] (main) realworld-quarkus 1.0.0 on JVM (powered by Quarkus 3.17.8) started in 3.854s. Listening on: http://0.0.0.0:8080\n2026-03-14 07:36:05,241 INFO  [io.quarkus] (main) Profile prod activated. \n2026-03-14 07:36:05,241 INFO  [io.quarkus] (main) Installed features: [agroal, cdi, hibernate-orm, hibernate-validator, jdbc-postgresql, narayana-jta, resteasy, resteasy-jackson, smallrye-context-propagation, vertx]\nApplication started successfully on port 8080\nRunning smoke tests...\n============================================================\nRealWorld API Smoke Tests\n============================================================\n\nWaiting for application to be ready...\nApplication is ready!\n\n--- Test: GET /tags ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'tags' key\n  PASS: Tags is a list\n\n--- Test: GET /articles ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'articles' key\n  PASS: Response has 'articlesCount' key\n  PASS: Articles is a list\n  PASS: articlesCount is a number\n\n--- Test: POST /users (Register) ---\n  PASS: Status is 201\n  PASS: Response has 'user' key\n  PASS: User has email\n  PASS: User has username\n  PASS: User has token\n  PASS: Email matches\n  PASS: Username matches\n\n--- Test: POST /users/login (Login) ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'user' key\n  PASS: User has token\n  PASS: Email matches\n\n--- Test: GET /user (Current User) ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'user' key\n  PASS: User has email\n  PASS: User has username\n\n--- Test: PUT /user (Update User) ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'user' key\n  PASS: Bio updated\n\n--- Test: GET /articles/feed ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'articles' key\n  PASS: Response has 'articlesCount' key\n\n--- Test: POST /articles (Create Article) ---\n  PASS: Status is 201\n  PASS: Response has 'article' key\n  PASS: Article has slug\n  PASS: Title matches\n  PASS: Article has tagList\n  PASS: Article has author\n  PASS: Article has createdAt\n\n--- Test: GET /articles/{slug} ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'article' key\n  PASS: Slug matches\n\n--- Test: GET /articles?author=smokeuser ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: articlesCount is 1\n\n--- Test: GET /articles?tag=dragons ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: articlesCount is 1\n\n--- Test: PUT /articles/{slug} (Update) ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Body updated\n\n--- Test: POST /articles/{slug}/favorite ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Favorited is true\n  PASS: favoritesCount is 1\n\n--- Test: DELETE /articles/{slug}/favorite ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Favorited is false\n  PASS: favoritesCount is 0\n\n--- Test: POST /articles/{slug}/comments ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'comment' key\n  PASS: Comment has id\n  PASS: Comment body matches\n\n--- Test: GET /articles/{slug}/comments ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'comments' key\n  PASS: Has at least 1 comment\n\n--- Test: DELETE /articles/{slug}/comments/{id} ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n\n--- Test: Register Celeb User ---\n  PASS: Status is 201\n\n--- Test: GET /profiles/celeb_smokeuser ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Response has 'profile' key\n  PASS: Username matches\n  PASS: Following is false\n\n--- Test: POST /profiles/celeb_smokeuser/follow ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Following is true\n\n--- Test: DELETE /profiles/celeb_smokeuser/follow ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Following is false\n\n--- Test: GET /tags (after article creation) ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n  PASS: Has dragons tag\n  PASS: Has training tag\n\n--- Test: DELETE /articles/{slug} ---\n  PASS: Status is 200\n\n============================================================\nRESULTS: 72 passed, 0 failed, 72 total\n============================================================\nAll smoke tests passed!\nSmoke tests finished with exit code: 0","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d54d9ac2-22a6-4fd0-85db-0f21ac49e7c7","uuid":"a982ae19-9fd6-40e0-8c02-8ed2379078f4"}
